item.description: [/b] Original song arranging & jamming.[/b] Rehearsal of songs for performance. Generally, newcomers, beginners,  intermediates and free style jamming starts at 2PM, and Rehearsal for Open mikes, shows around 2:30. Bring music sheets of your songs if possible. All musician levels welcome & encouraged. Lessons in theory or practice, music genres, or jamming if appropriate. [i]Directions will be emailed to attendees the night before or morning (by 10AM) of the meetup[/i].
